<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Alerta de Prazo</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      position: relative;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #cbe4de;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header img {
      width: 165px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fce4e4;
      border-left: 5px solid #e57373;
      position: relative;
    }
    .content h1 {
      color: #114658;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .content .alert-icon {
      width: 30px;
      height: auto;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #e57373;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #114658;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .footer img {
      width: 89px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .date {
      text-align: start;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #666;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://noodletop.com.br/publicftp/finalflow/logo.png" alt="FinalFlow Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="date">
        {{ data }}
      </div>
      <h1><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/e57373/error.png" alt="Alerta" class="alert-icon"/> Atenção, {{nome}}</h1>
      <p>Este é um alerta importante que você precisa saber. Por favor, leia com atenção.</p>
      <p><strong>Detalhes do Alerta:</strong></p>
      <p>{{mensagem}}</p>
      <a href="#" class="button">Saiba Mais</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 FinalFlow. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      {{!-- <img src="https://noodletop.com.br/publicftp/finalflow/mascote.png" alt="Mascote"> --}}
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
